{"tid":1287350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[關於76光復屯門公園] 自稱黃絲暴徒 有冇得諗","createTime":"2019-07-05T07:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T12:21:56.000Z","uid":22116,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b8365aa009fff728b44e64da559246ddfe3aeee8","tid":1287350,"uid":22116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:23:02.000Z","msg":"覺得好嘅請幫手推post<br />\n覺得唔好嘅請負皮 唔好推由個post沉<br />\n<br />\n因為個活動係連紅藍底政治冷感都會支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地當然可以話&quot;班黃屍終於做返件好事&quot; 但同時都焗佢地心底局部認同依班所謂嘅&quot;暴徒&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最最最重要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班親共派冇得騎劫活動拎光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n班親共派一痴埋黎 即刻被connected佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbetween, 黃絲暴徒只係個名, 大家記住唔好同人分享夢境"},{"pid":"ac01b4d5a307063204ed8ca9322f8089bb340a8f","tid":1287350,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:27:31.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvSJXSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvSJXSZ.png&h=0386e4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ccf959083890ac5acb60d03f8ee5d2d1dc14e02","tid":1287350,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"<i